lead_paragraph: Centre Jeronimo de la Fuente has had to withdraw from Argentina's squad to face New Zealand and Australia in the Rugby Championship in September after failing to recover from injury.

headline.print_headline: Argentina's De La Fuente Out of Tests in Australia, NZ
